      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "when the right conditions are fulfilled, things will turn out well on their own",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "彼は長年、影で努力を続けていたから、まさに凹き所に水溜まるで協力者が自然と現れた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「焦らなくても、凹き所に水溜まると言うし、準備さえ整えば結果は勝手についてくるよ」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "有望なベンチャー企業に資金が集まる様子を見て、凹き所に水溜まるとはよく言ったものだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "someone in bad circumstances will continue to accumulate difficulties",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "事業の失敗に家族の病気が重なり、凹き所に水溜まるように不幸が続いてしまった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「一度落ち目になると、凹き所に水溜まるで悪いことばかりが寄ってくるものだ」と彼は嘆いた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "不景気の煽りを受けて失業者がさらに困窮する現状は、まさに凹き所に水溜まるの構図だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
